title: NICOLA STURGEON SAYS THERE'S A REAL RISK OF A NO DEAL BREXIT
text:
NICOLA STURGEON SAYS THERE'S A REAL RISK OF A NO DEAL BREXIT 8:55pm BST - 00:38
Speaking at the Reuters Newsmaker event on 14th May 2018, Scotland's First Minister Nicola Sturgeon warns that there's a real risk of a no deal Brexit which would be 'catastrophic' for the UK.
